<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Explore the World - Global Health Explorers</title>
    <style>
        :root { --primary: #0f4c81; --secondary: #17a2b8; --dark: #212529; --light: #f8f9fa; --white: #ffffff; }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; }
        body { color: var(--dark); background-color: var(--light); line-height: 1.6; }
        header { background-color: var(--primary); color: var(--white); padding: 1rem 2rem; text-align: center; }
        .motto-banner { background-color: #fff3cd; color: #856404; text-align: center; padding: 0.5rem; font-weight: bold; }
        .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 3rem auto; padding: 2rem; background: var(--white); border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); border-top: 4px solid var(--secondary); }
        h1 { color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        h2 { color: var(--primary); margin: 2rem 0 1rem 0; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--secondary); padding-bottom: 0.25rem; }
        .back-btn { display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }
        .image-placeholder { background: #e2e8f0; width: 100%; height: 220px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border-radius: 6px; margin: 1rem 0; border: 2px dashed #cbd5e1; color: #64748b; font-weight: bold; }
        
        .country-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
        .metric-box { background: var(--light); padding: 1rem; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.95rem; border-left: 3px solid var(--secondary); }
        .metric-title { font-weight: bold; color: var(--primary); display: block; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="motto-banner"><strong>Learning Global Health Today, Leading Tomorrow</strong></div>
    <header><h1>Explore the World</h1></header>
    <main class="container">
        <a href="index.html" class="back-btn">← Back to Home</a>
        <p>Learn how public wellness metrics, healthcare delivery structures, and longevity variables differ across distinct nations and geographic regions.</p>
        
        <div class="image-placeholder">🗺️ [IMAGE: Global Health Indicators Interactive Mapping Graphic]</div>

        <!-- Canada -->
        <h2>🇨🇦 Canada</h2>
        <div class="country-grid">
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Demographics</span>Population: ~39 Million<br>Life Expectancy: ~82 Years</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Health Indicators</span>Universal publicly funded healthcare model system.</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Common Challenges</span>Healthcare delivery logistics across expansive remote/northern rural geography.</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Major Achievements & Facts</span>Pioneered deep modern insulin synthesis protocols; second-largest country landmass on earth.</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Japan -->
        <h2>🇯🇵 Japan</h2>
        <div class="country-grid">
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Demographics</span>Population: ~124 Million<br>Life Expectancy: ~84.5 Years</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Health Indicators</span>World-leading longevity metrics supported by universal statutory health insurance systems.</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Common Challenges</span>Managing healthcare resources for a rapidly aging demographic and declining birthrate.</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Major Achievements & Facts</span>Highly balanced ancestral dietary frameworks; highest proportion of centenarians globally.</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Norway -->
        <h2>🇳🇴 Norway</h2>
        <div class="country-grid">
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Demographics</span>Population: ~5.5 Million<br>Life Expectancy: ~83.2 Years</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Health Indicators</span>Extremely high universal human development index and mental wellness indicators.</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Common Challenges</span>Mental wellness tracking during extended seasonal northern winter periods.</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Major Achievements & Facts</span>Pioneered "Friluftsliv" (open-air living frameworks) to bolster community health balance.</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Brazil -->
        <h2>🇧🇷 Brazil</h2>
        <div class="country-grid">
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Demographics</span>Population: ~216 Million<br>Life Expectancy: ~76.2 Years</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Health Indicators</span>Operates the SUS (Sistema Único de Saúde)—the largest free universal healthcare engine worldwide.</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Common Challenges</span>Mitigating tropical insect-borne disease patterns across complex interior rainforest ecosystems.</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Major Achievements & Facts</span>Global leader in massive community vaccine distribution networks; contains the Amazon basin.</div>
        </div>

        <!-- India -->
        <h2>🇮🇳 India</h2>
        <div class="country-grid">
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Demographics</span>Population: ~1.43 Billion<br>Life Expectancy: ~70.1 Years</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Health Indicators</span>Dynamic scaling of digital health delivery models via massive mobile technology infrastructure.</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Common Challenges</span>Balancing density infrastructure and tracking air wellness profiles across mega-cities.</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Major Achievements & Facts</span>The pharmacy of the world (largest producer of affordable generic medications globally); home to ancient holistic Ayurveda practices.</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Kenya -->
        <h2>🇰🇪 Kenya</h2>
        <div class="country-grid">
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Demographics</span>Population: ~55 Million<br>Life Expectancy: ~67.5 Years</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Health Indicators</span>Rapidly expanding universal coverage tracks via community health worker systems.</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Common Challenges</span>Securing consistent, clean hydration assets across rural arid communities.</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Major Achievements & Facts</span>Pioneered mobile-money health funding applications; global capital of elite long-distance athletic running health.</div>
        </div>

        <!-- South Africa -->
        <h2>🇿🇦 South Africa</h2>
        <div class="country-grid">
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Demographics</span>Population: ~60 Million<br>Life Expectancy: ~65.3 Years</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Health Indicators</span>Advanced clinical research hubs managing comprehensive immunology monitoring programs.</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Common Challenges</span>Overcoming historical structural disparities in rural family medical resources.</div>
            <div class="metric-box"><span class="metric-title">Major Achievements & Facts</span>Successfully executed the world’s very first human heart transplant surgery in Cape Town (1967).</div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
